Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:02.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:06.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gatherall the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're on a journey in search of\NNaraku who has disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together, we've managed to\novercome many hardships,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but a dark shadow will cast over\nthe hearts of my friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you found the way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I'm trying to concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been at it since morning\nand it's getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, this forest must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a demon's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shucks! Did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Get rid of a useless\nthing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way! My motherbought it forme.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming... something evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:52.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At last! The master of this forest\nmakes his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon or an apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I can see it,\NI can get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:07.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit stalling and show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome to my Forest of Sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, that demon is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Gatenmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? You know Gatenmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the bane of my tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hearhe banded togetherwith\nlowly humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then got himself killed\nby a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that's a sharp sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:03.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That half-demon... was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was such a stupid ending\nto the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?\NThe smell of demon blood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You pesky moth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you wanna avenge Gatenmaru's death,\NI'll gladly take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Avenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whateverfor?\NHe deserved to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I could care less about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:42.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate moth demons like you\nand him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:42.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:58.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's entering my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...is being sucked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:24.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so uncouth to suck out\nhuman blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These days, my tribe likes\nto devour
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the heart and soul, shaking\nin fear and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't be so weak!\NHey Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:50.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whateveryou shout,\nthey cannot hear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Answerme!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:01.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By morning, a part of me shall\ntake hold of theirhearts and bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:06.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I test it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only way to break this curse\nis to defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall create nightmares foryou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:35.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you shall pour out your\nultimate fear and despairforme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! K-Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Kirara can handle him like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,maybe it's too early\nforhim to face battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku is very skilled\nwith his sickle and chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if anything should happen,\NI'll be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.\NI'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:09.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How fun! How fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you forget all your cares\nwhen you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMushin, why isn't\nmy fatherhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMushin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourfatherdid not want you to\nsee him part from this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Part from this life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:57.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many acorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buyo went in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This place is creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This miasma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota, run! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beyond that suffering awaits\nunfathomable despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:23.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall get an ample taste of\nyourfear and hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'd you do to those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just letting them dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans and demons alike...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all have fears that they suppress\ndeep down in theirhearts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which dreams can release.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We feed on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Release Kagome and the others now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahalf-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:01.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see yourfear\nso clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without your comrades,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you're so lonely,\nyou can't bearit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:11.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ljust don't like you making\nmy friends yourfodder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:19.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The unbearable fear of\nbeing alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall devourit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the one who's all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:57.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you destroy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll devourtheir souls
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:07.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and with theirbodies...\NI shall grow another self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that will spell YOURend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:15.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Being devoured by your\nformerfriends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that is the fate that awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:23.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you will be truly released\nfrom the fear of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The cocoon won't disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What can I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:13.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis! Rejoice forme!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I exterminated demons\nall by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exterminated demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fatherwill praise me, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's yourfault, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMushin!\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your Wind Tunnel has\nreached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don'tgo anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll find Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One more step...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come near!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's notexposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk... did you want so much\nto be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:08.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At the expense of\nyourfriends' lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all yourdoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cursing my grandfather\nwith the Wind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... I've been dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's unlike you to be dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were sleeping so soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been cramming too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:10.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!\NBlades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all there is\nto yourpowers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:35.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it so weak that a mere dream\ncould devourit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I misjudged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're gonna give up\nso easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll defeat Naraku alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:46.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come crying later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:57.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't let a moth demon\neat yourheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not a weak girl\nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!\NForgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must kill you,\noryou can't return to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is that, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you, then kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the only way to get\nyou back from Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't kill Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We mustget him back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... with me around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It only causes everyone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit rambling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's betterto stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're good at fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you afraid of!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:15.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you expose that hand once more,\NI'll cut it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you want to defeat Naraku\nand break the curse of the Wind Tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no place to be\nwasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're absolutely right, Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Shippo, you've been\ntrying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a thing to say\nat a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't win in your\nhuman form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd go without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can overcome any adversity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Guys!\NAtta way, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what MYfriends\nare made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're leaving this forest now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Overthere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The forest disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it was all an illusion\ncreated by Garamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We wasted so much time\nbecause of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:52.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without me around,\nyou guys are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Any complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's exactly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At least today,\nwe'll let itgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a way to put it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:11.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nevermind, Inuyasha.\NEveryone acknowledges what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I DO mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:19.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you really believe I saved you,\nat least say, "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:24.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, Kagome, as ourrepresentative,\nplease say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me... to SIT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Th-ank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa... it wasn't "sit."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:48.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well now, shall we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey Kagome!\NWhat'd you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon! Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:21:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:02.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:50.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Afterlosing my father, I had\ncontinued my training.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Powdery snow fell steadily{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:53.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and my body sank deeperand deeper\ninto the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:23:57.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there was someone who saved me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was his encounterwith\NKoyuki seven years ago?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She resembles that\nwoman of my memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did yourtears freeze into snow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:10.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Snow from Seven Years Past"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.07,0:24:13.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, she's not human!{\i0}
